:"2017-02-09T00:07:29.000Z","msg":"快d打啦，好悶呀.jpg"},{"pid":"37c4c94914bd16f5a15a8d2606bea91b1780fdcd","tid":113144,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:15:24.000Z","msg":"根本唔洗出兵<br />\n玩經濟戰電子戰，玩到支那乞米<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d129d51bb33ad3b302ad69cae81ea196a328f7f0","tid":113144,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:17:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中美開戰，連登仔就咪話想走得甩，實炸香港</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n炸香港做乜？炸左香港有咩好處？"},{"pid":"c918aa09b2e72584e87abbc1d5185ece0ff19db7","tid":113144,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477485776f530aef6ee03ea18166fae85fb4f3c3","tid":113144,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:23:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中美開戰，連登仔就咪話想走得甩，實炸香港</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n炸香港做乜？炸左香港有咩好處？</blockquote><br />\n實實實 實佢老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  香港又唔係戰略要地 炸黎做乜"},{"pid":"3b6b5bb9eab9fd5b2ed249df50a90414f66c9c58","tid":113144,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:35:53.000Z","msg":"10年中國都自爆左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf635e8c803226901801a09ea389fa7ba5e59ec","tid":113144,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:36:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中美開戰，連登仔就咪話想走得甩，實炸香港</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n炸香港做乜？炸左香港有咩好處？</blockquote><br />\n實實實 實佢老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  香港又唔係戰略要地 炸黎做乜</blockquote><br />\n你知唔知呢兩個國家打起嚟會炸埋印度俄羅斯南美etc.... 一堆國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n純粹因為我打完變廢墟費事你唔係之後變做最強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以結果打完核戰就係最後大少少既城市同國家都全部變晒廢墟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd84dae8b75c70b80b3546b6c1c1c54e4d946b29","tid":113144,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中美開戰，連登仔就咪話想走得甩，實炸香港</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6md9n2tg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6md9n2tg&h=b3b58c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n儲定三十萬買個避難所咪唔驚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a45a1d132d235e1adcc4973c289a9fa91ac9ad","tid":113144,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:49:00.000Z","msg":"而家打仗仲不停炸？<br />\n仲停留喺二戰思維"},{"pid":"622b659050d721143ccc46de52d1a4a4f5fc1fa0","tid":113144,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連到任先再吹啦"},{"pid":"c7a8e6eca15519fc6c11ab62ebdc5572fad124d9","tid":113144,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:58:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家打仗仲不停炸？<br />\n仲停留喺二戰思維</blockquote><br />\n講撚到你係佢地肚入邊條蟲？"}]}